data.text: Jonathan Hartley is a seasoned dating coach dedicated to empowering individuals in their romantic pursuits. With a wealth of experience and insight, he guides clients towards fulfilling relationships through personalized strategies and compassionate guidance. Jonathan's expertise lies in fostering confidence, communication skills, and self-awareness to help individuals navigate the complexities of modern dating with grace and authenticity.
